{"repo": "confident-ai/deepteam", "pull_number": 117, "instance_id": "confident-ai__deepteam-117", "issue_numbers": [114], "base_commit": "56c22c557fa45cbb0b962f4c50d6e8b787934987", "patch": "diff --git a/deepteam/cli/main.py b/deepteam/cli/main.py\nindex 60d5c1a6..e631872e 100644\n--- a/deepteam/cli/main.py\n+++ b/deepteam/cli/main.py\n@@ -59,7 +59,7 @@\n     GraphicContent,\n     PersonalSafety,\n ]\n-VULN_MAP = {cls().get_name(): cls for cls in VULN_CLASSES}\n+VULN_MAP = {cls.__name__: cls for cls in VULN_CLASSES}\n \n ATTACK_CLASSES = [\n     Base64,\n@@ -77,7 +77,8 @@\n     SequentialJailbreak,\n     BadLikertJudge,\n ]\n-ATTACK_MAP = {cls().get_name(): cls for cls in ATTACK_CLASSES}\n+\n+ATTACK_MAP = {cls.__name__: cls for cls in ATTACK_CLASSES}\n \n \n def _build_vulnerability(cfg: dict, custom: bool):\n", "test_patch": "", "problem_statement": "[Bug] CLI not working\nCLI doesn't work for a fresh installation of deepteam package.\n```\n$ uv run deepteam                                                                                                                                                                              \nTraceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"/xxxxxxxxxxxxxxx/.venv/bin/deepteam\", line 4, in <module>\n    from deepteam.cli.main import app\n  File \"/xxxxxxxxxxxxxxx/.venv/lib/python3.12/site-packages/deepteam/cli/main.py\", line 80, in <module>\n    ATTACK_MAP = {cls().get_name(): cls for cls in ATTACK_CLASSES}\n                  ^^^^^\nTypeError: Roleplay.__init__() missing 2 required positional arguments: 'persona' and 'role'\n```\n**Issue**: \n* Roleplay requires a few arguments: https://github.com/confident-ai/deepteam/blob/5f93cf0c630b1bc2d87c0286bdda1fd413356a30/deepteam/attacks/single_turn/roleplay/roleplay.py#L24-L32\n\n\n", "hints_text": "\n\n", "all_hints_text": "@penguine-ip Hey, I fix this issue please check and merge this https://github.com/confident-ai/deepteam/pull/117\n\n", "commit_urls": ["https://github.com/confident-ai/deepteam/commit/677834991f3cb0cc59997aea89394ba2ce017703", "https://github.com/confident-ai/deepteam/commit/a1965ab56a3c5394f880ef86d99ad14cd7574026"], "created_at": "2025-08-21T21:45:54Z"}
